OL,5, Government will take a "step back" from
OL,6, people's lives and pursue "a smaller   
OL,7, state", the PM's new top aide has said.
OL,9,FSteve Barclay told the Sunday Telegraph
OL,10,Fthat while public health interventions 
OL,11,Fand vast amounts spent in the pandemic 
OL,12,Fwere the right decisions, it was time  
OL,13,Ffor "a more enabling approach".        
OL,15,FThe PM made cabinet minister Mr Barclay
OL,16,Fhis new chief of staff last week.      
OL,18,FNo 10 says the prime minister will     
OL,19,Ffocus on domestic policy on a tour of  
OL,20,Fparts of the UK this week.             
